n></p>
<p>代码为</p>
<div class="language-java line-numbers-mode" data-ext="java"><pre v-pre class="language-java"><code><span class="token keyword">public</span> <span class="token keyword">static</span> <span class="token keyword">void</span> <span class="token function">reversePrint</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token class-name">String</span> str<span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token keyword">int</span> index<span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>
