<p>对应力扣题目 <a href="https://leetcode.cn/problems/reverse-linked-list/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">206. 反转链表 - 力扣（LeetCode）<ExternalLinkIcon/></a></p>
<div class="language-text line-numbers-mode" data-ext="text"><pre v-pre class="language-text"><code>输入：head = [1,2,3,4,5]
