<span class="token punctuation">}</span>
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><h3 id="e05-有序链表去重-力扣-82-题" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#e05-有序链表去重-力扣-82-题" aria-hidden="true">#</a> E05. 有序链表去重-力扣 82 题</h3>
<p>例如</p>
<div class="language-text line-numbers-mode" data-ext="text"><pre v-pre class="language-text"><code>输入：head = [1,2,3,3,4,4,5]
输出：[1,2,5]

