	<span class="token keyword">return</span> <span class="token number">1</span>
<span class="token punctuation">}</span>
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><h3 id="e07-合并多个有序链表-力扣-23-题" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#e07-合并多个有序链表-力扣-23-题" aria-hidden="true">#</a> E07. 合并多个有序链表-力扣 23 题</h3>
<p>例</p>
<div class="language-text line-numbers-mode" data-ext="text"><pre v-pre class="language-text"><code>输入：lists = [[1,4,5],[1,3,4],[2,6]]
输出：[1,1,2,3,4,4,5,6]
