<p>小顶堆（可删去用不到代码）</p>
<div class="language-java line-numbers-mode" data-ext="java"><pre v-pre class="language-java"><code><span class="token keyword">class</span> <span class="token class-name">MinHeap</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>
